.1, 1075.2]}, {"text": "through December 31, 2012, of which $415.5 million remains available at December 31, 2010. On February 1,", "bbox": [189.1, 1079.5, 1094.2, 1100.3]}, {"text": "2011, the Board of Directors authorized an additional $1 billion of common stock repurchases through", "bbox": [189.1, 1104.5, 1094.1, 1125.3]}, {"text": "December 31, 2012. Management has and may continue to establish prearranged written plans pursuant to", "bbox": [189.1, 1129.4, 1094.2, 1150.3]}, {"text": "Rule 10b5-1. A Rule 10b5-1 plan permits us to repurchase shares at times when we may otherwise be unable to", "bbox": [189.1, 1154.5, 1094.2, 1175.3]}, {"text": "do so, provided the plan is adopted when we are not aware of material non-public information.", "bbox": [189.1, 1179.5, 998.9, 1200.4]}, {"text": "Refer to Note 16 of our Consolidated Financial Statements for information related to our equity compensation", "bbox": [168.8, 1217.0, 1093.9, 1237.8]}, {"text": "plans.", "bbox": [143.8, 1242.0, 193.0, 1262.9]}, {"text": "Dividend Policy", "bbox": [143.8, 1292.1, 285.1, 1312.9]}, {"text": "On December 8, 2010 our Board of Directors declared a cash dividend of $0.07 per share payable on", "bbox": [168.8, 1329.6, 1094.2, 1350.4]}, {"text": "December 31, 2010. During 2010, the Company’s Board of Directors declared quarterly cash dividends of", "bbox": [143.8, 1354.6, 1094.2, 1375.5]}, {"text": "$0.06 per common share payable on March 31, 2010, June 30, 2010 and October 14, 2010. On December 9,", "bbox": [143.8, 1379.5, 1094.2, 1400.4]}, {"text": "2009, our Board of Directors declared a cash dividend of $0.06 per share payable on December 30, 2009. The", "bbox": [143.8, 1404.6, 1094.0, 1425.4]}, {"text": "35", "bbox": [608.6, 1478.2, 629.5, 1499.0]}]}